<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV77">
<l>eṭṭumeṭṭu meṭṭumāyo rēḻumēḻu mēḻumā</l>
<l>yeṭṭumūṉṟu moṉṟumāki niṉṟavāti tēvaṉai</l>
<l>yeṭṭiṉāya pētamōṭi ṟaiñciniṉṟa vaṉpeya</l>
<l>reṭṭeḻuttu mōtuvārkaḷ vallarvāṉa māḷavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who continuously prostrate with the eight different [limbs]</l>
<l>the primeval Lord—</l>
<l rend="indent">who, being the eight [plus] eight [plus] eight [realities]</l>
<l rend="indent">and the seven [islands], seven [mountains], and the seven [oceans],</l>
<l rend="indent">is the eight [plus] three [plus] one [Ādityas] —</l>
<l>and recite the eight-syllabled [mantra],</l>
<l>will be capable of ruling over heaven!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
